After installing node and npm install CLI:
npm install -g @angular/cli
npm ERR! code E403 npm ERR! 403 Forbidden: @angular/cli@latest

Solution
https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/issues/8612

Update .npmrc file(under user/suresh-negi

cafile=C:\Users\suresh-negi\pvcs_cert
registry=http://registry.npmjs.org/
proxy=http://suresh-negi:&win82017@inggn1-07pr01-int-1-0.ip.mrshmc.com:8888
strict-ssl=false

//suresh-negi:&win82017  username:pass
